snippet.textDisplay: Vird tere naamon ka ho raha hai ku ba ku.... Very powerful words... The last parts of this make me think of the entire Universe and everything within and beyond; the galaxies, the stars, the sun, the moon, the celestial beings, the angels all praising their Creator, Allah. It does something inexplicable to my soul. It's very reassuring and reaffirming whenever I listen to it. Abida Parveen is blessed and inimitable. Her voice is proof of her devotion. May she be forgiven and may us all be forgiven.
